@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@scenarioVersion = {{$timestamp}}

### Cadastro do usuario 1 (dono das contas) -> 201 sem corpo
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria da Silva",
  "email": "maria.contas.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Login do usuario 1 -> 200 com token
# @name loginUser1
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria.contas.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Cadastro do usuario 2 (usado para validar isolamento) -> 201 sem corpo
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Joao Pereira",
  "email": "joao.contas.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Login do usuario 2 -> 200 com token
# @name loginUser2
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao.contas.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Criacao de conta com dados validos (usuario 1) -> 201 com a conta criada
# @name createAccount
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Conta corrente",
  "type": "checking",
  "institution": "Banco X",
  "initialBalance": 100.5
}

### Criacao de conta com name vazio -> 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "",
  "type": "checking"
}

### Criacao de conta com type fora do enum -> 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Conta invalida",
  "type": "bitcoin"
}

### Listagem de contas do usuario 1 -> 200 com apenas as contas do usuario 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Listagem de contas do usuario 2 -> 200 lista vazia (isolamento)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

### Busca por id da conta do usuario 1 -> 200 com a conta
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{createAccount.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Busca por id de conta inexistente -> 404 account.not.found
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Busca da conta do usuario 1 usando o token do usuario 2 -> 404 account.not.found (isolamento)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{createAccount.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

### Atualizacao da conta do usuario 1 -> 200 com a conta atualizada
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{createAccount.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Conta corrente atualizada",
  "initialBalance": 250.75
}

### Atualizacao com dados invalidos (name vazio) -> 422
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{createAccount.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": ""
}

### Atualizacao da conta do usuario 1 usando o token do usuario 2 -> 404 account.not.found (isolamento)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{createAccount.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Tentativa de invasao"
}

### Exclusao de conta inexistente -> 404 account.not.found
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/accounts/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Exclusao da conta do usuario 1 usando o token do usuario 2 -> 404 account.not.found (isolamento)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{createAccount.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

### Exclusao da conta do usuario 1 -> 204 sem corpo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{createAccount.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}
